OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FJade Wright has lived through every
OL,8,Fparents' worst nightmare - finding out
OL,9,Fsomething she did in pregnancy caused
OL,10,Flifelong harm to her children. But it
OL,11,Fwasn't her fault.
OL,13,FJade is epileptic, and was prescribed
OL,14,Fa medication called Sodium Valproate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
