OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1754377071
OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FIt's an effective treatment for the
OL,8,Fcondition and has helped save
OL,9,Fthousands of lives over the years -
OL,10,Fbut it's also been linked to birth
OL,11,Fdefects in thousands of babies, whose
OL,12,Fmothers were prescribed the drug
OL,13,Fduring pregnancy - but never warned of
OL,14,Fthe risks to their unborn children.
OL,16,F"Betrayed isn't even the word -
OL,17,Fbecause you trust your doctors, don't
OL,18,Fyou?" Jade, from Lancashire, explains.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
