OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"When I found out that this medication
OL,8,Fcould cause learning difficulties I
OL,9,Fwas nearly sectioned, I didn't want to
OL,10,Fbe here anymore, because I blamed
OL,11,Fmyself.
OL,13,F"Even though I knew I asked all the
OL,14,Fright questions, it doesn't take away
OL,15,Fthe guilt.
OL,17,F"I felt like a failure, like I
OL,18,Fshouldn't be a mum."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/18
