OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FAll three of Jade's children were born
OL,8,Fwith signs of Foetal Valproate
OL,9,FSyndrome - which can include a range
OL,10,Fof complex disabilities including
OL,11,Flearning difficulties, speech and
OL,12,Flanguage delay, sensory processing
OL,13,Fdisorder, heart and kidney defects,
OL,14,Fand deformation of the spine or limbs.
OL,16,FJade says she repeatedly asked doctors
OL,17,Fabout the safety of taking the
OL,18,Fmedication with all three of her
OL,19,Fpregnancies, but was only told of a
OL,20,Fslightly increased risk of spina
OL,21,Fbifuda.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/18
