OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FNow, Jade worries constantly about her
OL,8,Fchildren's future. Her eldest son
OL,9,FTyler is the worst affected - and Jade
OL,10,Fbelieves it's because doctors
OL,11,Fincreased her dosage of Sodium
OL,12,FValproate while she was pregnant.
OL,14,FTyler shares his story in his own
OL,15,Fwords here:
OL,17,FJade describes seeing the impact on
OL,18,Fher children as "devastating to watch"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/18
