OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1754377071
OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"This has rewritten their lives,
OL,8,Fespecially Tyler. It's taken so much
OL,9,Faway from him, he'll never have a
OL,10,Fmeaningful job, and never be able to
OL,11,Fsupport himself, he'll never be able
OL,12,Fto drive.
OL,14,F"I don't really like to think about
OL,15,Fit, but is he ever going to get the
OL,16,Fopportunity to get married, to have
OL,17,Fkids? It's just not realistic, and
OL,18,Fit's not fair... all because I wasn't
OL,19,Ftold.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
