OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"It's a huge scandal, it's a huge
OL,8,Finjustice - and it needs to be put
OL,9,Fright doesn't it?"
OL,11,FBut putting it right has proved to be
OL,12,Fpolitically complicated.
OL,14,FIn 2020 an independent review, chaired
OL,15,Fby Baroness Julia Cumberlege, strongly
OL,16,Fcriticised the industry and regulators
OL,17,Fand recommended that the Government
OL,18,Fset up a redress scheme to compensate
OL,19,Fall affected children and their
OL,20,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
