OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FIn 2024, another report, this time by
OL,8,Fthe Patient Safety Commissioner Dr
OL,9,FHenrietta Hughes, set out exactly how
OL,10,Fthe compensation scheme could work,
OL,11,Fand also suggested the Government make
OL,12,Fquicker interim payments.
OL,14,FBut the one year anniversary of that
OL,15,Freport came and went in February 2025.
OL,16,FI spoke to Dr Hughes at the time, and
OL,17,Fshe was clearly frustrated that no
OL,18,Fprogress had been made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/18
