OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"My message to the Government one year
OL,8,Fago was 'Get on with it!'" she told
OL,9,Fme. "And although the Government has
OL,10,Fchanged my message remains the same.
OL,12,F"Waiting for redress doesn't put the
OL,13,Fsuffering of those who have been
OL,14,Fharmed on pause, they need help right
OL,15,Fnow."
OL,17,FNow, parliament has once again risen
OL,18,Ffor its summer recess, with still no
OL,19,Fannouncement being made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/18
