OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FFor Janet Williams and Emma Murphy,
OL,8,Fwho have helped to lead the campaign
OL,9,Ffor Sodium Valproate compensation,
OL,10,Fit's another kick in the teeth for
OL,11,Ftheir disabled children, and the
OL,12,Fhundreds of families they represent.
OL,14,F"The weight of anxiety that this is
OL,15,Fcausing on families is utterly
OL,16,Fridiculous" says Janet, "and I think
OL,17,Fpoliticians have got to realise what
OL,18,Fthat wait feels like."
OL,20,FSo what's going on?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
