OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FNow all those things can certainly be
OL,8,Ftrue - we've seen with the Thalidomide
OL,9,Fand the infected blood scandals among
OL,10,Fothers that redress schemes are not
OL,11,Fsimple, even with a huge amount of
OL,12,Fpolitical goodwill.
OL,14,FThere are always questions of
OL,15,Feligibility, burdens of proof,
OL,16,Fchallenging administration issues. For
OL,17,FSodium Valproate there's the added
OL,18,Fcomplication that we don't know for
OL,19,Fsure how many children were impacted,
OL,20,For how severely.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
