OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FBut Janet and Emma are worried that
OL,8,Fthere's a bigger barrier to
OL,9,Fcompensation victims of the scandal:
OL,10,Fmoney.
OL,12,F"We get the impression that they don't
OL,13,Fwant to do this, because they're
OL,14,Fworried about how much this might
OL,15,Fcost," says Janet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
