OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FAnd both women say they've heard that
OL,8,Fthey were very close to announcing a
OL,9,Fcompensation scheme before the last
OL,10,FGeneral Election, but the then-
OL,11,Fgovernment had to prioritise another
OL,12,Fscandal instead.
OL,14,F"We have spoken to a senior member of
OL,15,Fthe Conservative Government" explains
OL,16,FEmma.
OL,18,F"In that meeting it was stated that it
OL,19,Fwas actually a toss up between sodium
OL,20,Fvalproate and contaminated blood to
OL,21,Fget compensation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
