CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F394A1754377071
OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"Tthink that could have been their
OL,8,Fthinking, to pit people's families up
OL,9,Fagainst each other, that is just
OL,10,Fabhorrent. These are real children
OL,11,Fwith disabilities, real adults, real
OL,12,Flives. We're not just data."
OL,14,FNow, Labour are in charge, and the
OL,15,FPrime Minister has assured victims of
OL,16,Fthe scandal that this is "obviously a
OL,17,Freally important matter".
OL,19,FBut they have been in power for over a
OL,20,Fyear now, and campaigners anxieties
OL,21,Fare mounting.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/18
