OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FThis MP, who has been fighting for
OL,8,Fcompensation ever since she came into
OL,9,Fparliament, admits she feels
OL,10,Ffrustrated by the lack of progress.
OL,12,FWe have asked the Government for
OL,13,Fanother update on when they will
OL,14,Frespond to the Hughes Report and set
OL,15,Fout the details of a compensation
OL,16,Fscheme.
OL,18,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,19,Fspokesperson said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
