OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"The harm caused by sodium valproate
OL,8,Fcontinues to be felt today. Our
OL,9,Fsympathies are with those affected and
OL,10,Fwe are fully focused on how best to
OL,11,Fsupport patients and prevent future
OL,12,Fharm.
OL,14,F"This is a complex area of work and
OL,15,Fthe government is carefully
OL,16,Fconsidering the Patient Safety
OL,17,FCommissioner's recommendations in full.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/18
