OL,3,CMum 'nearly sectioned' over
OL,4,Cprescription drug that disabled her
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"Health Minister Baroness Gillian
OL,8,FMerron met patients affected and has
OL,9,Fcommitted to providing a further
OL,10,Fupdate."
OL,12,FSo exactly when things will change for
OL,13,Ffamilies waiting for redress remains a
OL,14,Fbit of an unknown.
OL,16,FOne thing is clear though when you
OL,17,Fspeak to women like Jade, Janet and
OL,18,FEmma - this is a battle they aren't
OL,19,Fwilling to lose.
